The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | SC on turbans
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     SC on turbans
                            
	New Delhi, May 13: The Supreme Court today gave a sympathetic hearing to a Sikh forum that had complained about the ban on turbans in schools in France, but said its jurisdiction did not extend beyond India.                                                                                                                                                                          
